1133
02:34:28,125 --> 02:34:30,874
Sweep away all sorts ofbad characters!

1134
02:34:31,416 --> 02:34:34,165
Destroy our enemy!

1135
02:34:38,208 --> 02:34:40,957
Uncover the black gangs!
Cut offthe vacious hands!

1136
