Duan Xiaolou is vicious!

1142
02:36:03,416 --> 02:36:06,040
Duan Xiaolou and Cheng Dieyi
are anti-Party elements!

1143
02:36:06,958 --> 02:36:12,040
Down with Duan Xiaolou!
Down with Cheng Dieyi!

1144
02:36:13,041 --> 02:36:16,249
