ofthe laboring masses.

1169
02:37:59,791 --> 02:38:01,540
Keep going! Get to the point!

1170
02:38:02,958 --> 02:38:04,415
Say it! Say it!

1171
02:38:05,958 --> 02:38:07,582
Down with Cheng Dieyi!

1172
02:38:16,541 --> 02:38:17,332
