Heroic and encouraging

1218
02:44:47,125 --> 02:44:58,457
The soldiers of Han have invaded

1219
02:45:01,416 --> 02:45:11,415
The songs of Chu can be heard on all sides

1220
02:45:12,666 --> 02:45:15,790
My king,

1221
