give me your precious sword
to end my life.

1222
02:45:50,541 --> 02:45:57,082
No! You mustn't do that!

1223
02:45:59,125 --> 02:46:04,874
- My king, give me your precious sword.
- No! You mustn't...

1224
02:46:13,458 --> 02:46:14,582
