At sixteen, I am a nun.

1228
02:46:45,708 --> 02:46:48,707
My hair is shorn at youth's prime.

1229
02:46:49,000 --> 02:46:50,749
I am by nature a boy...

1230
02:46:51,000 --> 02:46:52,207
